    <item>
      <title>20歳を過ぎてから英語を学ぼうと決めた人たちへ</title>
      <link>https://meganii.com/blog/2012/05/19/study_english/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 19 May 2012 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://meganii.com/blog/2012/05/19/study_english/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;amz-container&#34; style=&#34;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:20px;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;amz-left&#34; style=&#34;float:left; margin:0 20px 0;&#34;&gt;
